{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2e99-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"41304"},"text":"§ 41304.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Effective periods and amendments, modifications, suspensions, and revocations of permits","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2e9a-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"General","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Transportation may prescribe the period during which a permit issued under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t49/s41302"},"text":"section 41302 of this title","children":[],"tail":" is in effect. After notice and an opportunity for a hearing, the Secretary may amend, modify, suspend, or revoke the permit if the Secretary finds that action to be in the public interest."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2e9b-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Suspensions and Restrictions","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Without a hearing, but subject to the approval of the President, the Secretary—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2e9c-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" may suspend summarily the permits of foreign air carriers of a foreign country, or amend, modify, or limit the operations of the foreign air carriers under the permits, when the Secretary finds—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2e9d-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/b/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the action is in the public interest; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2e9e-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/b/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" the government, an aeronautical authority, or a foreign air carrier of the foreign country, over the objection of the United States Government, has—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2e9f-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/b/1/B/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" limited or denied the operating rights of an air carrier; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2ea0-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/b/1/B/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" engaged in unfair, discriminatory, or restrictive practices that have a substantial adverse competitive impact on an air carrier related to air transportation to, from, through, or over the territory of the foreign country; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2ea1-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to make this subsection effective, may restrict operations between the United States and the foreign country by a foreign air carrier of a third country.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2ea2-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Illegal Importation of Controlled Substances","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2ea3-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" in consultation with appropriate departments, agencies, and instrumentalities of the Government, shall reexamine immediately the fitness of a foreign air carrier that—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2ea4-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/c/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" violates the laws and regulations of the United States related to the illegal importation of a controlled substance; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2ea5-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/c/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" does not adopt available measures to prevent the illegal importation of a controlled substance into the United States on its aircraft; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2ea6-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" when appropriate, shall amend, modify, suspend, or revoke the permit of the carrier issued under this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2ea7-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s41304/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Responses","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"An interested person may file a response with the Secretary opposing or supporting the amendment, modification, suspension, or revocation of a permit under subsection (a) of this section.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idcbbb2ea8-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/272/s1/e"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–272, § 1(e)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-07-05"},"text":"July 5, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/1127"},"text":"108 Stat. 1127","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idcbbb2ea9-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"historicalAndRevision","id":"idcbbb2eaa-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:table","attrib":{"width":"50%","id":"idcbbb2eab-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:colgroup","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":